  "texts": [
    "By adding new data to the Blockchain, a smart contract at the access layer interacts directly with the Blockchain.",
    "At the same time, this contract examines the data to see if it contains the proper characteristics for inclusion in the Blockchain.",
    "The data is sent back to the smart devices.",
    "If an emergency situation arises (as determined by smart contract regulations) 61, the smart device will send an alarm straight to the Hospital Control Unit (HCU) to guarantee patient safety.",
    "The patients, through this way, can see the results that are shown by the smart devices."
  ],
